{"ID":"20240121140054-1wn766k","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20240121140054-1wn766k","title":"安防系统-闲鱼","type":"doc","updated":"20240121142500"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240121140055-u01plr3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240121140055-u01plr3","updated":"20240121140114"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.环境搭建"}]},{"ID":"20240121140127-ix1x95r","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240121140127-ix1x95r","updated":"20240121142500"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240121140740-6buxn9y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240121140740-6buxn9y","updated":"20240121140848"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.在目录下输入 创建Django项目"}]},{"ID":"20240121140817-ax2d8j8","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240121140817-ax2d8j8","updated":"20240121140830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"django-admin startproject security_system\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240121140817-kp7jox5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240121140817-kp7jox5","updated":"20240121140900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 2.创建Django应用"}]},{"ID":"20240121140907-hax1exv","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240121140907-hax1exv","updated":"20240121140917"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":" python manage.py startapp data_processing\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240121140908-vi9ia4z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240121140908-vi9ia4z","updated":"20240121140934"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" "},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240121140934-k6pylcc.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20240121140908-baxfe84","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240121140908-baxfe84","updated":"20240121142321"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 3.在data_processing文件夹下的models.py添加数据库模型"}]},{"ID":"20240121142323-uohquh3","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240121142323-uohquh3","updated":"20240121142331"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"from django.db import models\n\n# 更新后的User模型\nclass User(models.Model):\n    username = models.CharField(max_length=100, unique=True)\n    phone_number = models.CharField(max_length=20, unique=True)\n    password = models.CharField(max_length=50)\n    face_image = models.ImageField(upload_to='user_faces', blank=True, null=True)  # 允许为空，不是所有用户都需要上传面部图像\n\n    def __str__(self):\n        return self.username\n\nclass SensorData(models.Model):\n    temperature = models.FloatField()\n    humidity = models.FloatField()\n    co_level = models.FloatField()\n    smoke_level = models.FloatField()\n    timestamp = models.DateTimeField(auto_now_add=True)\n\n    def __str__(self):\n        return f\"{self.timestamp} - Temp: {self.temperature}, Humidity: {self.humidity}, CO: {self.co_level}, Smoke: {self.smoke_level}\"\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240121140909-bskfbj6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240121140909-bskfbj6","updated":"20240121142356"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 4.在settings中添加app应用"}]},{"ID":"20240121142335-qdnxsqp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240121142335-qdnxsqp","updated":"20240121142408"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240121142407-cwm21b2.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]}]},{"ID":"20240121142335-skfy141","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240121142335-skfy141","updated":"20240121142423"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.生成新的迁移文件来反映这些模型的变化"}]},{"ID":"20240121142336-a0urmla","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240121142336-a0urmla","updated":"20240121142433"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"python manage.py makemigrations data_processing\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240121142336-sxtwn5u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240121142336-sxtwn5u","updated":"20240121142453"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.应用迁移"}]},{"ID":"20240121142454-5q9z88i","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240121142454-5q9z88i","updated":"20240121142500"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"python manage.py migrate\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240121142338-p1gn4a8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240121142338-p1gn4a8"}},{"ID":"20240121142338-uv6zy7r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240121142338-uv6zy7r"}},{"ID":"20240121142338-8krmkae","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240121142338-8krmkae"}},{"ID":"20240121142336-w00ndzp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240121142336-w00ndzp"}},{"ID":"20240121142337-agux6fg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240121142337-agux6fg"}},{"ID":"20240121140909-v5lvxfx","Type":"No